title: Mountainous Forest Landscape
description: A scenic view of rolling hills covered with dense green forests. The landscape features a variety of trees, with a mix of dark green foliage and patches of lighter green. In the background, more hills can be seen, creating a layered effect, with a soft blue sky and distant mountains visible in the far background.

title: Serene Lake Landscape
description: A tranquil lake surrounded by lush green forests and mountains in the background. The water is calm and reflects the blue sky and surrounding scenery, creating a picturesque and peaceful atmosphere.

title: Coastal Landscape
description: A scenic view of a coastline featuring rocky cliffs and gentle waves lapping at the shore. The landscape is illuminated by warm sunlight, highlighting the textures of the cliffs and the blue hues of the ocean.

title: Aerial View of Coastal Wetlands
description: An aerial view showcasing a vibrant coastal wetland area. The image features a network of winding waterways surrounded by lush green vegetation and patches of yellowish land. The contrasting colors of the turquoise water and the greenery create a striking visual, highlighting the intricate patterns formed by the natural landscape.

title: Scenic Landscape with Trees
description: A picturesque landscape featuring several large trees with lush green foliage, set against a bright blue sky with fluffy white clouds. The ground is covered in vibrant green grass and patches of colorful wildflowers, creating a serene and inviting natural scene.
